Man: LOOK OUT!

00:36.965 --> 00:39.758
THE FORCE OF THAT WATER, IT'LL
JUST BREAK YOUR COLLARBONE,

00:39.758 --> 00:42.034
SMASH YOUR TEETH.

00:42.034 --> 00:43.137
[ MAN SHOUTS ]

00:43.137 --> 00:45.448
THE IS BERING SEA FISHING, MAN.

00:45.448 --> 00:48.586
♪ I'M-A GIVE YOU A SECOND
JUST TO CATCH YOUR BREATH ♪

00:48.586 --> 00:50.379
♪ 'CAUSE I CAN SEE THAT ♪

