RIGHT NOW,
I'M JUST ONE POT AT A TIME.

00:56.793 --> 00:58.689
KEEP 'EM SAFE, GET IT STACKED.

00:58.689 --> 01:00.827
♪♪

01:00.827 --> 01:05.000
♪ I'VE GOT EVERY REASON
